OL,3,CLottery winners who scooped #2.7m
OL,4,Cjackpot in 1995 finally fulfil dream
OL,6,FA couple who bought three racehorses
OL,7,Fafter scooping #2.7 million on the
OL,8,FNational Lottery have completed their
OL,9,Fdream of visiting all 59 racecourses
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FElaine and Derek Thompson, who turned
OL,13,Ftheir love of racing into a full-time
OL,14,Fhobby after their 1995 win, celebrated
OL,15,Fat Ludlow Racecourse earlier this week
OL,16,Fwith a race named after them.
OL,18,FMr and Mrs Thompson, from Newcastle,
OL,19,Fdecided to indulge in racehorses ahead
OL,20,Fof the usual houses, cars and holidays
OL,21,Fwhen they hit the Lotto jackpot.
