OL,6,FBut Mr Thompson said luck has not
OL,7,Falways been on their side, with one of
OL,8,Fthe horses earning the nickname Sick
OL,9,FNote as it seemed to develop a cough
OL,10,Fbefore each race meeting and never won
OL,11,Fa race.
OL,13,FThe couple's third racehorse, Richmond
OL,14,FLady, who was shared with a friend,
OL,15,Fdid go on to win at Exeter, but Mr
OL,16,FThompson said it was such a foggy day
OL,17,Fthat they did not see it crossing the
OL,18,Ffinishing line.
