OL,6,FHe said: "We have always loved horse
OL,7,Fracing, it's such a great atmosphere
OL,8,Fand over the years I have learned
OL,9,Fwhich trainers to follow.
OL,11,F"We decided after our National Lottery
OL,12,Fwin to travel the UK and visit every
OL,13,Fracecourse in the country. Originally,
OL,14,Fthere were 61 but two have closed down
OL,15,Fover the years.
OL,17,F"Ludlow is our 59th and we have
OL,18,Fdefinitely saved a lovely course for
OL,19,Four last one."
