OL,6,FMrs Thompson said: "Owning racehorses
OL,7,Fis a pretty pricey business ` there
OL,8,Fare a lot of costs involved.
OL,10,F"One horse, a beautiful grey named
OL,11,FBalfour Lady, needed a lot of shoes. I
OL,12,Fwould say she had more shoes than
OL,13,FImelda Marcos whilst we owned her.
OL,15,F"It was lots of fun but we eventually
OL,16,Fdecided it was probably best to focus
OL,17,Fon being punters and stick to our
OL,18,Fplacepots.
