OL,6,F"Finishing our tour of the 59
OL,7,Fracecourses at Ludlow is really
OL,8,Fspecial. It is such a fabulous
OL,9,Fracecourse, small and intimate which
OL,10,Fis what we love."
OL,12,FThe couple, who have been married for
OL,13,F45 years, sponsored the Elaine and
OL,14,FDerek Thompson Celebration Chase at
OL,15,Fthe Shropshire racecourse.
